）全球08:00【全球疫情汇总】据新浪实时统计，截至3月14日8点，除中国（包括港澳台地区）以外，海外新冠肺炎累计确诊61425例，死亡2197例，治愈6447例。
) As of 0800 hours March 14, a total of 61,425 new cases of pneumonia had been diagnosed, 2,197 had died and 6,447 cases had been cured, excluding China (including Hong Kong, Macao and Taiwan).
新增0表示当天暂未宣布数据。
A new 0 indicates that data were not announced for that day.
数据来源：新浪08:00【世卫组织：欧洲已成为新冠肺炎“大流行”的“震中”】世卫组织总干事谭德塞当天在例行记者会上说，目前123个国家和地区累计向世卫组织报告超过13.2万例新冠肺炎确诊病例，死亡病例已超过5000例，“这是一个悲剧性的节点”。
More than 132,000 confirmed cases of new crown pneumonia have been reported to the WHO from 123 countries and territories, and more than 5,000 deaths have been reported, "said WHO Director-General Stan Desai at a regular news conference.
07:57【国际足联：建议推迟定于3月和4月举行的所有国际赛事】美国08:45【美国累计确诊新冠肺炎病例已上升至1992例】据环球网报道，根据美国约翰斯·霍普金斯大学公布的实时疫情数据，截至北京时间14日上午8时30分，美国已有累计1992例新冠肺炎确诊病例。
07: 57 [FIFA: Recommended postponement of all international tournaments scheduled for March and April] The cumulative number of confirmed cases of New Crown Pneumonia in the United States has risen to 1992, according to real-time data released by Johns Hopkins University in the United States.
其中，43例死亡病例。
Of these, 43 were fatal.
08:00【特朗普宣布美国进入紧急状态，启动500亿美元资金抗疫】紧急状态，触发《斯塔福法案》，为向各州和自治市提供更多联邦资金铺平道路。
08: 00 [Trump announces a state of emergency in the United States, triggers a $50 billion epidemic, triggers the Stafford Act, and paves the way for more federal funding for states and municipalities.
特朗普提到的主要措施包括在各州建立临时医疗设施，减少医院及研究中心向政府提出申请时的行政手续，给予医生更大的诊断灵活度，与私营机构合作加快新冠病毒测试以应对测试量提升缓慢的瓶颈，并将提供直通车测试中心。
Among the main measures Trump has mentioned are the establishment of temporary health-care facilities in the states, reducing administrative procedures for hospitals and research centers to apply to the government, giving doctors greater diagnostic flexibility, working with the private sector to speed up testing for the new crown virus to address the bottleneck of slow increase in testing, and providing through-train testing centers.
受特朗普发布会提振，周五美股大幅收高。
US stocks closed sharply higher on Friday, buoyed by Trump's news conference.
08:00【特朗普：中国提供的数据帮忙了美国抗“疫”】08:00【特朗普：我非常有可能进行新冠病毒检测】美国总统特朗普在记者会上表示，我非常有可能会进行新冠病毒检测。
08: 00 [Trump: The data provided by China has helped the US fight the plague] 08: 00 [Trump: I have a good chance of getting tested for the new crown virus.
当被记者问到何时时，特朗普称，会很快。
When asked by reporters when, Trump said, it would be quick.
08:00【美国新增414例新冠肺炎确诊病例累计1678例】00:12【苹果2020年开发者大会将以线上形式举行】伊朗08:00【为切断病毒传播链，伊朗出动军队“清街”】过去一天伊朗境内新增新冠肺炎感染者1289例，累计11364例，新增死亡85例，累计514例。
08: 00 U.S. 414 New Cases of New Crown Pneumonia Confirmed Cases 00: 12 [Apple 2020 Developer Conference to be held online] Iran 08: 00 Iranian troops clear the streets to cut off the virus transmission chain 1 289 new cases of pneumonia were reported in Iran over the past day, with a total of 11,364 new cases and 85 new deaths totalling 514.
武装部队总参谋长巴盖里宣布，为切断病毒传播链，军队上街，确保全国所有商业中心、街道和市场关闭。
The Chief of General Staff of the armed forces, Sergei Bageri, announced that to cut off the virus's transmission chain, the army was on the streets to ensure the closure of all commercial centres, streets and markets throughout the country.
危地马拉08:00【危地马拉首次确诊新冠肺炎病例】患者是一名24岁的男子，刚从意大利北部返回危地马拉，这名男子没有明显病征。
Guatemala 08: 00 [Guatemala First Confirmed Coronary Pneumonia] The patient is a 24-year-old man who has just returned to Guatemala from northern Italy and does not show any visible signs of illness.
危地马拉政府此前已宣布将新冠肺炎从黄色预警上调为红色预警，禁止所有欧洲以及韩国和伊朗公民入境，并对来自洪都拉斯、墨西哥、巴拿马和哥斯达黎加的旅客采取至少一周的集中隔离。
The government has previously announced an increase in Crown Pneumonia from a yellow alert to a red alert, a ban on all European and South Korean and Iranian citizens, and at least one week of concentrated isolation for travellers from Honduras, Mexico, Panama and Costa Rica.
乌拉圭08:00【乌拉圭首次报告新冠肺炎确诊病例】4名确诊患者本月3日至6日从意大利米兰入境乌拉圭，目前身体状况平稳，在家接受隔离。
Uruguay 08: 00 [Uruguay first reports confirmed cases of pneumonia] Four confirmed cases entered Uruguay from Milan, Italy, from March 3 to 6 and are now in stable condition and isolated at home.
乌拉圭政府13日宣布了一系列防控措施，包括取消举办音乐节等大型活动、足球比赛不设观众等。
Uruguay announced on the 13th a series of control measures, including the cancellation of major events such as music festivals, football matches without spectators.
委内瑞拉08:00【委内瑞拉首次确诊新冠肺炎病例2名患者均有欧洲旅行史】其中一名41岁的委内瑞拉女性近期曾前往美国、意大利和西班牙旅行。
Venezuela 08: 00 [Venezuela First Confirmed New Crown Pneumonia] Two patients have a history of European travel. One 41-year-old Venezuelan woman recently traveled to the United States, Italy and Spain.
另一名男性患者今年52岁，近期曾去过西班牙。
Another male patient, 52, has recently been to Spain.
这两个确诊病例都在米兰达州。
Both confirmed cases are in Miranda.
厄瓜多尔08:00【厄瓜多尔出现首例新冠肺炎死亡病例累计确诊病例达23例】该患者是一名71岁女性，于2月14日从西班牙回到厄瓜多尔，因为呼吸困难而就医，之后一直在重症监护室接受治疗，于当地时间13日不治身亡。
Ecuador 08: 00 [Ecuador's first cumulative confirmed case of pneumonia death] The patient, a 71-year-old woman who returned to Ecuador from Spain on 14 February, was treated for respiratory distress and has since been treated in intensive care unit, where she died 13 days local time.
波兰07:52【波兰宣布进入公共卫生紧急状态】总理莫拉维茨基宣布，为防止新冠肺炎疫情扩散，从3月14日开始，全国进入公共卫生紧急状态。
Poland announces public health emergency Prime Minister Kristen Moravitsky declared a public health emergency on March 14 to prevent the spread of the outbreak of pneumonia in the New Crown.
加拿大08:00【加拿大新冠肺炎确诊病例上升至157例】从”至尊公主”号邮轮撤回的人员中，已发现2例确诊病例。
Canada 08: 00 [Canadas New Crown Pneumonia confirmed case rises to 157 cases] Two confirmed cases have been found among those withdrawn from the MV Princess Supreme.
以色列08:00【以色列新冠肺炎确诊病例达143例拟建3座方舱医院】大多数患者已住院，少数患者在家中接受隔离治疗，3名患者病情危重，3人康复，至今没有死亡病例。
Israel 08: 00 [Israel Crested Pneumonia Confirmed 143 Cases Proposed for Three Flat Cabin Hospitals] Most of the patients are hospitalized, a small number of patients are treated in isolation at home, three patients are in critical condition and three have recovered, and there have been no deaths to date.
以色列国防军定于下周开始建立三处临时救护中心，类似方舱医院，总共有三千个床位，用以接纳潜在的轻症患者居住和治疗，以便为重病患者腾出医院空间。
The Israel Defense Forces are scheduled to begin next week the construction of three temporary ambulance centres, similar to the square-cabin hospital, with a total capacity of 3,000 beds for the accommodation and treatment of potential light patients in order to free up hospital space for seriously ill patients.
伊拉克08:00【伊拉克新增10例新冠肺炎确诊病例累计确诊93例】其中9人死亡，24人痊愈。
Iraq 08: 00 Confirmed 10 Cases of New Crown Pneumonia: A cumulative total of 93 confirmed cases: 9 died and 24 recovered.
伊拉克卫生部仍在对疑似病例进行隔离观察与实验室检查。
The Iraqi Ministry of Health is still conducting isolated observation and laboratory examinations of suspected cases.
埃及08:00【埃及新冠肺炎确诊病例增至93例】埃及卫生与人口部宣布确认新增13例新冠肺炎病例，全部为之前确诊病例的接触者。
Egypt 08: 00 The Egyptian Ministry of Health and Population has announced the confirmation of 13 new cases of new crown pneumonia, all from contacts with previously confirmed cases.
13个新增病例中包括5个本土病例和8例不同国籍的外国人。
The 13 new cases include 5 indigenous cases and 8 foreigners of different nationalities.
卡塔尔08:00【卡塔尔新增58例新冠肺炎确诊病例累计确诊320例】这些新增病例大部分都是此前确诊病例的密切接触者，之前已经处于隔离状态。
Qatar 08: 00 [Qatar has a cumulative total of 320 confirmed cases of new crown pneumonia] Most of these new cases are in close contact with previously confirmed cases and have previously been isolated.
卡塔尔卫生部呼吁所有与确诊病例有过接触的人员速到指定医院接受医疗检查，居民也应加强自我防护意识，不要恐慌。
The Ministry of Health of Qatar calls on all persons who have come into contact with confirmed cases to come to designated hospitals for medical examination, and residents should be more aware of self-protection and not panic.
沙特08:00【沙特新增24例新冠肺炎确诊病例累计确诊86例】苏丹08:00【苏丹卫生部确认唯一一名新冠病毒感染者已死亡】感染者是一名50岁苏丹籍男性，于两周前有阿联酋旅行经历。
Saudi Arabia 08: 00 Confirmed 24 New Crown Pneumonia Confirmed Cases Sudan 08: 00 [Sudan's Ministry of Health confirms that the only person infected with the New Crown Virus who has died is a 50-year-old Sudanese man who travelled to the United Arab Emirates two weeks ago.
患者出现疑似症状后在苏丹首都喀土穆的一家私立医院接受了隔离治疗和两次检测，检测结果均为阴性。
The patient was quarantined and twice tested negative at a private hospital in the Sudanese capital, Khartoum, for suspected symptoms.
12日，患者去世后，医护人员对从其尸体提取的样本再次进行检测，结果为阳性。
12, after the death of the patient, medical personnel from his body to take samples of the re-testing, positive results.
患者家属和密切接触者已经被隔离。
Family members and close contacts have been isolated.
意大利08:00【意大利新增新冠肺炎确诊病例2547例新增死亡250例】累计确诊达17660例。
Italy 08: 00 2547 new confirmed cases of pneumonia in Italy: a cumulative total of 17,660 confirmed cases.
西班牙08:30【累计确诊5232例，已经宣布进入国家紧急状态】其中2659例出现在马德里地区，累计死亡133。
Spain 08: 30 [cumulative confirmed 5,232 cases, has been declared a state of emergency "of which 2,659 occurred in the Madrid region, cumulative deaths 133.
08:00【西班牙新冠肺炎确诊病例增至4334例】马德里将继续建临时医院，加泰罗尼亚请求封锁首都马德里确诊病例2659例。
08: 00 Confirmed cases of pneumonia in Spain increase to 4334 Madrid will continue to build temporary hospitals, and Catalonia has requested a blockade of 2,659 confirmed cases in the capital Madrid.
德国08:00【德国新增671例确诊病例累计3062例】累计死亡5例。
Germany 08: 00 Cumulative total of 3062 new confirmed cases in Germany 5 cases.
奥地利08:00【奥地利新冠肺炎确诊病例累计达504例】法国08:00【法国新增新冠肺炎确诊病例785例　卢浮宫等景点关闭】累计确诊新冠肺炎病例3661例，较前一天增长近800例，总计死亡病例79例。
Austria 08: 00 Confirmed Cases of New Crown Pneumonia France 08: 00 [France New Crown Pneumonia confirmed 785 cases of closure of scenic spots such as Louvre Palace etc. Cumulatively 3,661 new cases of pneumonia were confirmed, an increase of nearly 800 cases from the previous day, bringing the total number of deaths to 79.
即日起全国范围内禁止举行超过100人的集会活动。
More than 100 people are now banned from holding rallies across the country.
英国08:00【英国新增208例新冠肺炎确诊病例，累计798例】累计死亡病例10例。
Britain has 208 new cases of confirmed cases of New Crown Pneumonia, with a cumulative total of 798 deaths.
爱尔兰08:00【爱尔兰新增20例新冠肺炎确诊病例累计确诊90例】丹麦08:02【丹麦3月14日12点起将关闭边境】央视新闻消息，当地时间3月13日，据丹麦广播电视台报道，3月14日12点，丹麦边境将关闭，飞机、渡轮和火车运输将全部或部分关闭。
Ireland 08: 00 [Ireland: 20 New Cases Confirmed New Crown Pneumonia] Denmark 08: 02 Denmark will close its border on March 13 (Danish Radio Television) -- The Danish border will be closed at 12: 00 on March 14 and aircraft, ferry and train transport will be closed in whole or in part, DNK reported.
边境检查将持续到4月13日。
Border checks will continue until 13 April.
08:00【丹麦新增127例新冠肺炎确诊病例累计确诊801例】有23人住院，其中4名是重症患者。
08: 00 [801 cumulative confirmed cases of newly diagnosed pneumonia in Denmark] 23 people are hospitalized, 4 of whom are seriously ill.
挪威08:00【挪威累计确诊750例新冠肺炎病例】但是根据不断更新数据的《世界之路报》(VG)称，有973人被确诊。
Norway 08: 00 [Norway Cumulatively Identifies 750 Cases of Newly Coronary Pneumonia] But 973 people have been diagnosed, according to VG, which keeps the data up to date.
冰岛08:00【冰岛新增19例新冠肺炎确诊病例累计确诊128例】拉脱维亚08:00【拉脱维亚累计确诊18例新冠肺炎病例政府宣布进入紧急状态】希腊08:00【希腊新增73例新冠肺炎确诊病例累计确诊190例】在新增的73例感染者中，11人近期并无境外旅游经历；有9人居住在雅典及周边地区。
Iceland 08: 00 Cumulatively Confirmed Cases of New Crown Pneumonia in Iceland 08: 00 Latvia Cumulatively 18 Cases of New Crown Pneumonia Confirmed in Latvia The Government has declared a state of emergency Greece 08: 00 Greece has confirmed a cumulative total of 73 new cases of pneumonia 11 of the 73 new infections have no recent overseas travel experience; 9 live in Athens and surrounding areas
爱沙尼亚08:00【爱沙尼亚新增51例新冠肺炎确诊病例累计确诊68例】马来西亚08:00【马来西亚新增新冠肺炎确诊病例39例累计确诊197例】是自疫情暴发以来，日确诊病例数量最多的一天。
Estonia 08: 00 [Accumulation of 68 confirmed new cases of crowns pneumonia in Estonia] Malaysia 08: 00 [Malaysia has a cumulative total of 197 confirmed cases of new crown pneumonia in Malaysia] The highest number of confirmed cases per day since the outbreak.
